ys\"\n| Debby Ryan\n| \"[[List of Jessie episodes#ep5|One Day Wonders]]\"\n|-\n| \"Best Year\"\n| Debby Ryan\n| \"[[List of Jessie episodes#ep40|Why Do Foils Fall in Love?]]\"\n|-\n| \"We're Burning Up\"\n| [[Jessie J]]\n| \"Punch Dumped Love\"\n|}\n\n== Notes ==\n{{Reflist|group=note}}\n\n== References ==\n{{Reflist|refs=\n\n<ref name=\"Hollywood Reporter\">{{cite web|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/live-feed/disney-channels-jessie-premiere-posts-242864|title=Disney Channel's 'Jessie' Premiere Posts Record Ratings|date=October 1, 2011|work=Hollywood Reporter}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"upfront\">{{cite web|url=http://www.disneychannelmedianet.com/DNR/2011/dc_kids_fam_2011_upfront.doc|title=Disney Channel, Disney XD and Disney Junior Upfront 2011|publisher=Disney Channel Medianet|date=March 16, 2011|accessdate=April 7, 2011}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"debby on Jessie\">{{cite web|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=5Ku5qZeC83Q |title=Debby Ryan Gives Details on Her New Show \"Jessie\"|date=April 13, 2011|accessdate=April 16, 2011}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"production\">{{cite web|url=http://www.disneychannelmedianet.com/DNR/2011/JES_060911.doc|title=Disney Channel Announces Start Of Production On \"Jessie,\" A New Comedy Series Starring Debby Ryan|accessdate=June 9, 2011|url-status=dead|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130921055440/http://www.disneychannelmedianet.com/DNR/2011/JES_060911.doc|archivedate=September 21, 2013}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"IMDb.com\">{{cite web|url=https://www.imdb.com/name/nm0250518/|title=Pamela Eells \u2013 IMDb|accessdate=October 10, 2011|work=IMDb.com}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"SheKnows.com\">{{cite web|url=http://www.sheknows.com/entertainment/articles/841915/meet-jesse-the-next-disney-channel-supershow|title=Meet Jessie, the next Disney channel superstar|date=September 19, 2011|work=SheKnows.com}}</ref>\n\n<ref name=\"Star-Telegram\">{{cite web|url=http://www.star-telegram.com/2011/10/05/3419330/disney-star-is-happy-that-shes.html#tvg|title=D